Save as Docker format
++++++++++++++++++++
docker build -t myimage:latest .
docker save myimage:latest -o myimage.tar (myimage.tar   (Docker format)


Save as OCI format (important difference)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
docker buildx build --output type=oci,dest=myimage.tar .
myimage.tar   (OCI format)
